OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775477469
OL,3,CWoman, 54, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries in head-on crash
OL,6,FA woman has suffered life-threatening
OL,7,Finjuries in a head-on crash in County
OL,8,FDurham.
OL,10,FPolice were called at 8:20pm on
OL,11,FSaturday (4 April) to a two-vehicle
OL,12,Fcollision on Middridge Road, in Newton
OL,13,FAycliffe, involving a Skoda Octavia
OL,14,Fand Peugeot 3008.
OL,16,FThe cars are believed to have been
OL,17,Ftravelling in opposite directions when
OL,18,Fthey crashed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
