PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775477469
OL,3,CWoman, 54, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries in head-on crash
OL,6,FA 54-year-old woman, the driver of the
OL,7,FPeugeot, suffered life-threatening
OL,8,Finjuries and was taken to Darlington
OL,9,FMemorial Hospital.
OL,11,FOn Sunday evening, Durham Constabulary
OL,12,Fsaid her condition in hospital was
OL,13,Fdescribed as life-threatening.
OL,15,FThe driver of the Skoda, a 31-year-old
OL,16,Fman, was arrested on suspicion of
OL,17,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,18,Fdriving, driving while under the
OL,19,Finfluence of drugs, and possession of
OL,20,Fa controlled drug.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
