OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775477469
OL,3,CWoman, 54, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries in head-on crash
OL,6,FHe was taken into police custody where
OL,7,Fhe remained on Sunday evening. Three
OL,8,Fpassengers who were travelling in the
OL,9,FSkoda were uninjured.
OL,11,FOfficers would like to speak to anyone
OL,12,Fwho witnessed the incident, or anyone
OL,13,Fwho might have dashcam footage.
OL,15,FAnyone with information should call
OL,16,Fthe force on 101, quoting incident
OL,17,Fnumber 453 of 4 April.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
